{
  "stem": "23131.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So if the Judenrat had to tell somebody from my neighbors, or somebody at the street, you have to be, at 5 o'clock, at work, and you go to work here and here, come to the Judenrat, get your instructions, and go to work.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I had to go and give the message, because there was no other way of communicating with those people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a messenger.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] in Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had knew somebody that worked there, and he was in-- the head of the Judenrat, and he gave me that job.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Laufki ?] Glauberman.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] I did not have the privileges what my-- my stepbrother had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had much more privileges.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after a while you'll see that he had the privileges.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because of-- as of May 8, when we were slaughters, and it was the first [NON-ENGLISH], on account of him with his schein, with his identification, we remained alive.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That you'll have to come to work at 5 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Be here and here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That you have to be at 10 o'clock, here and here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Come to the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They have-- they have to send you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could not say no, because the Judenrat was ordered by-- by the SS, by the Nazis, by the Gebietskommissar.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do you know who was the Gebietskommissar?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you know his name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The worst that I hated, that it was Werner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the other one I knew, too, but I forgot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In fact, he was-- he had a trial in Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know the leader-- the [? born ?] leader that were there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they went for the trial to be witnesses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I know Werner, because his dogs I remember best.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was his--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
